{"tid":2153462,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧：中共威脅捷克主權","createTime":"2020-08-12T14:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T14:16:25.000Z","uid":278587,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6bd875157ae2d342344bdbba726a455a3fd154","tid":2153462,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】到了捷克訪問的美國國務卿蓬佩奧，批評中國共產黨威脅捷克的自由和主權。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧和捷克總理巴比什會晤後見記者。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧指，捷克和歐洲以及世界很多其他自由國家，都開始意識中國共產黨對她們的威脅，他特別提到去年五月，32個國家在布拉格就達成網絡安全框架，保障5G網絡安全，讚揚巴比什為了保護國民作出重要決定。蓬佩奧認為要保障自由國家的價值觀，摒棄不可靠的網絡。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧今次中歐和東歐之行，除了討論美軍在歐洲的部署，亦會商討如何對抗中俄兩國的勢力。他又提到，中俄兩國都想更多參與捷克的能源、基建和通訊建設，認為讓中國和俄羅斯國企參與興建杜科瓦內核電站，將會危及捷克的主權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401520&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7RSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=cda10d50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401520&h=1b7c392b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401520</a>"},{"pid":"2bd237fc0ff5be77de31874395daf9b9dc9cf8ed","tid":2153462,"uid":283912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:09:24.000Z","msg":"Pompeo 2024<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d8281a25b11d8d9f6f4c8eafc3e2080552d3b6","tid":2153462,"uid":277702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:11:02.000Z","msg":"佢真係好勁，周圍走去拉攏盟友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a5c036e8e8d5cc7e2af7ace7eed0673d2967d8","tid":2153462,"uid":127955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:11:43.000Z","msg":"有POST 話<br />\nPRAG 反共。<br />\n但整體捷克撐中反共爭持緊。"},{"pid":"271fa3973f2c135d953371cce1db4335dbd3db19","tid":2153462,"uid":134323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"日日十點見到蓮佩奧"},{"pid":"a7f55c039b9d5b0eb0870c8b94014092357e9095","tid":2153462,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:15:44.000Z","msg":"Global connector<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2476bf5ab9dcd13e8def053d0bcf578e23aa32","tid":2153462,"uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"pompeo日日出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等緊你下一份制裁名單"}]}